  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "**Is this a bug report or feature request?**\r\n* Feature Request\r\n\r\n**What should the feature do:**\r\nSince multiple filesystems are not recommended, there should be a way to restrict namespaces tp accessing only certain folders in Ceph FS. This is supported by ceph: http://docs.ceph.com/docs/mimic/cephfs/client-auth/#path-restriction but rook is not allowing to provide credentials for the mount.\r\n\r\n**What is use case behind this feature:**\r\nAllow multiple users use same ceph filesystem and protect their data from each other\r\n\r\n",
